As you know I have been using Seint cream makeup since 2017!
As my skin matures, my makeup keeps up with the changes.

It’s time to ditch powder & liquid ladies 🖤

Not to mention, all of my makeup comes in 1 easy compact.  It’s perfect for saving time, vacations, and everything in between.

I’d love to introduce you if you’re ready for something easier (and better) in your morning routine ❤️

Makeup Story! 
After weight gain and a bout with depression I lost myself.  I didn’t feel worthy of pretty things. 
I put myself on the back burner. 
When I started to lose weight and get back to me, I found this makeup in that transition. 
I put it on and felt good about myself.
It was the perfect combination of getting back to ME between weightloss and a new makeup routine. 
This journey brought out a whole new me as a matter of fact!
I realized that I could share this with other women and help them feel that same spark that I did. 
I realized that beauty is something that radiates from the inside. 
Confidence and self worth should be the real goal no matter what the scale reads. 
6 years later I still get that same feeling. 
I have zero makeup experience and can still rock this. 
Yes, it is just makeup, but it has been a confidence builder for me in more ways than one.
I would love to share it with you!

Another throw together win. 👊🏻🥦🍗
